data.description: Welcome home. This home offers 3 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 nice sized bathrooms.  When you enter this home, you are greeted by well preserved cherrywood flooring.  The separate formal dining room offers plenty of space to have a quiet dinner for one or two or a family dinner, either way, you will appreciate and love this gracious sized dining room.  As you proceed further inside this lovely home, you come to an open concept kitchen that with custom stained cabinets and attractive granite countertops.  You will receive a full appliance package to include a range oven, dishwasher, microwave, fridge and ice-maker line.  There is a breakfast area off the kitchen that has wonderful sunlight and is a perfect place to sit and have a cup of tea or coffee or simply just read.  The extra-large family room has a step-down feature that creates a feeling of charm and elegance along with the hardwood flooring.  The extra large family room makes it great for for movie night or party night, whichever you chose, there is space.  The upstairs of this home accommodates the bedrooms, all spacious and ready for its new owner.  The owner’s suite has a walk-in closet with a window and a view to the front of the house.  The owner’s suite offers multiple decoration and furniture layout options, whether you have a California King or a full-sized bed, you can't lose with the size of this room.  How about creating a sitting room?  There is room for that tool. The secondary bedrooms are large enough to accommodate Queen sized beds. The upstairs features a huge laundry room with a shelf for all your laundry detergent and other laundry requirements and the second bathroom is a great size.  This home has been treated with love and you can feel that from the time you walk in.  The backyard features lots of space for you to grow a garden, vegetable or flowers and, it provides privacy for those times you just want to sit outside and decompress from a hard day’s work.  Whatever you want, you can find it in this home.
